\id PHP  - Dobu NT [dob] -Papua New Guinea 1985 (web version -2013) 
\h PILIPAI 
\toc1 Me Pilipai ꞌIdi Leta Paulo ꞌIꞌetoladina 
\toc2 Pilipai 
\toc3 Pi 
\mt1 ME PILIPAI ꞌIDI LETA  
\mt1 PAULO ꞌIꞌETOLADINA  
\ip Lowa Paulo ꞌiloguguya ꞌasa Pilipai ꞌena, nate waine Lidia ꞌina ꞌasa, ga Yesu ꞌana toemisao sena gote ꞌena Paulo nuwana siꞌewena. Wate tuta nina deliya ꞌimiyami ꞌana oboboma sietunenama, ga manuna ꞌigwausowala, ga leta gete ꞌena ꞌilokagutoki ꞌediya.  
\ip ꞌEbweu yage ꞌiemataluwedi ꞌaene geyaꞌabo weyala, manuna Yesu nuwanuwana be siegosigosiyana leleleya.  
\c 1  
\s1 Lokagutoki  
\p
\v 1 \x * \xo 1:1 \xt Gu 16:1, 16:12-40\x*ꞌAboꞌagu ta Timoti maꞌiyagu ꞌaguiguinuwa Toꞌetoseyana Yesu manuna, ꞌimi leta ꞌaꞌetoladinawa ꞌomi me Pilipai Yesu Keliso ꞌina toekalesiyao, be wate ꞌimi toanuganao be ꞌimi dikoniyao maꞌemiyao.  
\v 2 Tamada Yaubada ta ꞌInapwana Yesu Keliso ꞌidi obobomega wada miya gwausowala.   
\s1 Paulo ꞌina sidasida me Pilipai manudi  
\p
\v 3 Tuta yauna Yaubada ꞌena yalokagutoki, ꞌabo tuta nina yanuwami,  
\v 4 ta ma igu gwausowala manumi ꞌigu sidasidao ꞌediya,  
\v 5 be ma igu lokagutoki ꞌama lemao ꞌemiyega ꞌalobalobadi, tetela boboꞌana ꞌana simanaꞌunuyega ga batuwa.   
\p
\v 6 \x * \xo 1:6 \xt Pi 2:13\x*Wate ma igu emisa ꞌaene Yaubada ꞌina guinuwa boboꞌadi niꞌatu ꞌemiya ꞌieꞌalena be tauna ꞌida losaloni, maꞌetamo Yesu Keliso ꞌina ꞌasiyata sinabwana ꞌenaya.  
\v 7 Onaꞌaiꞌaila, ꞌilobwenena be manumi toꞌase yalotolotoona nadigega, manuna ꞌomi nuwagu waꞌewena, manuna ꞌomi maꞌegwao Yaubada ꞌilemelemeda gete tuga deliya yamiyamiya, ta ꞌilemelemeda wate tetela boboꞌana ꞌana eꞌita be ꞌana ꞌebe ewaiwai ꞌediya.   
\p
\v 8 Yaubada wate ꞌimwalatonigu ꞌaene Yesu Keliso ꞌina obobomega nuwanuwagu ꞌomi,  
\v 9 \x * \xo 1:9 \xt Kol 1:9-10\x*ta ma igu sidasida manumi be ꞌaene ꞌimi eobooboboma ꞌisinasinabwa, ma imi sinasinapu be ma imi mwalatoi,  
\v 10 \x * \xo 1:10 \xt Pi 2:15-16\x*be ꞌenega yage boboꞌadi wada esinuwedi, be Keliso ꞌina ꞌasiyata maꞌetamo ꞌenaya adelimi boboꞌami ta ꞌesasemi,  
\v 11 ta ma imi guinuwa boboꞌadi Yesu Keliso ꞌina waiwaiyega, manudi tomota Yaubada sida tupui be sida ꞌawa eseese.   
\s1 Paulo ꞌina ꞌatetagwala Keliso ꞌenaya  
\p
\v 12 \x * \xo 1:12 \xt 2 Ti 2:9\x*Gosegwao, nuwanuwagu be wada mwalatoni ꞌaene mwau nidi niꞌatu yalobedi ꞌediyega tetela boboꞌana ꞌiꞌelelewana tomota yaudi ꞌediya,  
\v 13 ꞌenega sena gete ꞌenaya Sisa ꞌina tolosaiyao be tomota maiboꞌadi niꞌatu sinonona ꞌaene Keliso manuna sisaꞌugu deliya.  
\v 14 Ta wate tasidao yaudi ꞌigu miya deliya siꞌitena, ꞌenega sietaetapewa ꞌInapwana ꞌina guinuwa ꞌena, ta Yaubada ꞌina ona sisimasimane ma idi ꞌatepatu.   
\p
\v 15 ꞌAina tologuguyao eꞌipiꞌipiyega siloguloguguya Keliso manuna, ta ꞌaidi wate obobomega siloguloguguya,  
\v 16 taudi siobobomegu ꞌaene ꞌaboꞌagu deliya yamiyami tetela boboꞌana ꞌana eꞌita manuna,  
\v 17 ta esi toeꞌipiꞌipi nidi nuwanuwadi be sigienuwa mwauyegu gete tuga deliya yamiyami, ꞌenega ꞌidi kaboega Keliso tetelina siguguyae taudimo ꞌidi gilagata manuna.   
\p
\v 18 Ta tuwa tuga Keliso nina tetelina ꞌana loguguya yauna manuna yagwaugwausowala, ꞌeguma kaboega nai onaꞌaiꞌailega.  
\v 19 \x * \xo 1:19 \xt 2 Ko 1:10-11\x*Ta wate yada gwausowala, manuna yamwalamwalatoni ꞌaene Yesu Keliso yaluyaluwana ꞌina lema ꞌenega, be ꞌimi sidasidao manugu ꞌediyega, sida liꞌamigu miyamwau gete ꞌenega.   
\p
\v 20 \x * \xo 1:20 \xt 1 Pi 4:16\x*Wate ꞌaboꞌagu ma igu emisa ta ma igu nuwayaina ꞌaene geyaꞌabo yaomayamaya, ta esi yanuwayaina ꞌaene ma igu ꞌatepatu gete tuga ta tuta yauna Keliso ꞌana esana yada giesinabwa, nai ꞌigu miya baleꞌu mayawasigu ꞌenega, nai ꞌigu mwawasa ꞌenega.   
\p
\v 21 \x * \xo 1:21 \xt Ga 2:19-20\x*Onaꞌaiꞌaila, ꞌigu miya baleꞌuya nate Keliso maꞌiyagu, ta esi ꞌigu mwawasa ꞌenaya loeposeyana Keliso ꞌenega yalobai.  
\v 22 ꞌEguma baleꞌuya yamiyami ꞌigu guinuwao boboꞌadi Keliso manuna siapweapwesa, ꞌenega nigeya yamwalamwalatoni toꞌase nuwanuwagu be yaesinuwe.  
\v 23 \x * \xo 1:23 \xt 2 Ko 5:8\x*Onaꞌaiꞌaila, yage ꞌeluwa ꞌediyega ꞌadi esinuwa ꞌeguya mwau wawasae. Nuwanuwagu be baleꞌu gete yapilisine be Keliso maꞌiyagu ꞌamimi, nate ꞌebe gwausowala sinabwana.  
\v 24 Ta esi ꞌilobwenegu be baleꞌuya yada miyami be ꞌenega yada lemelememi.  
\v 25 ꞌEnega yamwalatoi ꞌaiꞌailina ꞌaene ꞌomi maꞌegwao tada miyami be yada lememi be wada gwausowala ꞌimi emisa Keliso ꞌena manuna,  
\v 26 be wate ꞌigu ayausa limana ꞌemiya manuna wada gwausowala sinabwana, nate Yesu Keliso ꞌina lema ꞌedaya manuna.  
\v 27 \x * \xo 1:27 \xt Ep 4:1\x*Ta wada ꞌitaꞌiꞌisimi ꞌaene ꞌimi guinuwao ꞌediyega tomota Keliso tetelina sida ꞌawaboboꞌane, ꞌenega ꞌeguma yayausimi, nai ꞌeguma yamiyaila, tuwa tuga tetelimi boboꞌana yada noono ꞌaene ma imi ꞌatetagwala watoolo paꞌala, ta ma imi nuwanuwa leleleya ga ꞌenega waetaetapewa tetela boboꞌana ꞌana emisa manuna,  
\v 28 ta geyaꞌabo wate wamatamatauta ꞌami talauwalao ꞌediya. Gete manuna taudi sida mwalatoi ꞌaiꞌaili ꞌaene sida esilae, be ꞌomi ꞌami ꞌetoseyana wada loba Yaubada ꞌenega.   
\p
\v 29 \x * \xo 1:29 \xt Gu 5:41\x*Manuna Yaubada niꞌatu ꞌitagwala ꞌemiya be Keliso ꞌena waemiemisa, be tauna wate manuna wada ꞌelouya,  
\v 30 \x * \xo 1:30 \xt 1 Te 2:2\x*nadigega ꞌaboꞌagu ꞌigu losaiya Keliso manuna be ꞌigu ꞌelouyao waꞌitedi, ta gete tuga wanonodi, ta ꞌomi wate ꞌimi losaiya be ꞌimi ꞌelouyao nadigega walobaꞌesedi.   
\c 2  
\s1 Nuwamwaꞌuta  
\p
\v 1 Mwaꞌadega, Keliso sawesawenaya ꞌigie ꞌatepatuda, nai ꞌina oboboma ꞌigie etapeweda? Mwaꞌadega, Yaluyaluwa Tabuna sawesawenaya ꞌiegosigosiyaneda, be ꞌenega taeoboobobomeda be taꞌatenuwa ꞌoleꞌoleyeda?  
\v 2 ꞌEguma nadigega, ꞌilobwenemi be wanuwanuwa leleleya, be waeoboobobomemi ꞌomi, yaluyaluwami be ꞌatemi ꞌidi eꞌebweu ꞌenega, be ꞌimi oboboma gete manuna yada gwausowala ꞌaiꞌaila.  
\v 3 \x * \xo 2:3 \xt Lo 12:10, 16\x*Geyaꞌabo wanuwanuwa tuꞌe nai waeꞌipiꞌipi, ta esi wanuwa mwaꞌuta, be gosemiyao ꞌadi esanao wagilagasidi.  
\v 4 \x * \xo 2:4 \xt 1 Ko 10:24, 33\x*Ta geyaꞌabo taumimo ꞌimi guinuwa manuna wanuwanuwa, ta esi gosemiyao ꞌidi miya boboꞌana manuna wada nuwanuwa.   
\p
\v 5 ꞌIlobwenemi be ꞌimi nuwanuwao Yesu Keliso ꞌina nuwanuwa nadigega.  
\v 6 \x * \xo 2:6 \xt Yo 1:1-2\x*Yesu nina Yaubada, ta geya nuwana be ꞌietoloina,  
\v 7 \x * \xo 2:7 \xt 2 Ko 8:9\x*ta esi Yaubada ꞌina esaesa ꞌipilisinena, ga ꞌitubuwa baleꞌuya, ga ꞌieꞌaliꞌei tomota ꞌaboꞌada ꞌatuwa.  
\v 8 \x * \xo 2:8 \xt Ib 5:8, 12:2\x*ꞌEnega wate ꞌina nuwamwaꞌuta ꞌenega, taunamo ꞌitagwalena ga ꞌimwawasa kelose ꞌenaya.   
\p
\v 9 \x * \xo 2:9 \xt Ep 1:20-21; Ib 1:3-4\x*ꞌEnega Yaubada Yesu ꞌigituꞌeyena ta ꞌana esana wate ꞌigituꞌeyena esana maiboꞌana etanidiya,  
\v 10 \x * \xo 2:10 \xt Lo 14:11\x*be ꞌenega ꞌana esana manuna me galewa be me baleꞌu ta tomwawasao wate, maiboꞌada tada bwagobwago,  
\v 11 \x * \xo 2:11 \xt Lo 10:9\x*be tada ꞌawaꞌaiꞌaila ꞌaene Yesu Keliso tauna ꞌInapwana nina, be wate Tamada Yaubada tatupui.   
\s1 Maedana me baleꞌu manudi  
\p
\v 12 Gosegwao ꞌomi ematamatana ꞌalemi. Lowa mataguya waematamatana, ta gete tuga ꞌemiyega yamiya ꞌedasola, ta tuga maꞌetamo waematamatana ꞌaiꞌaila. ꞌEnega ꞌilobwenemi be Yaubada wamataute be wate watoo waiwai be ꞌina ꞌetoseyana waloba,  
\v 13 \x * \xo 2:13 \xt 1 Te 2:13\x*manuna Yaubada nina ꞌatemiya ꞌietaetapewa, be ꞌaene tauna ꞌina nuwenuwega ꞌomi wanuwanuwa be waguiguinuwa.  
\v 14 Ta ꞌimi paisewa ꞌediya ma imi ꞌatetagwala wada guinuwa, ta geyaꞌabo ma imi logwautoyasa walomulomugi,  
\v 15 be ꞌaene ꞌomi Yaubada natunao boboꞌami ta ꞌesasemi, ta nigeya ꞌebweu wate ꞌimi toꞌumalinamo, be me baleꞌu ꞌidi mayale ꞌomi. Manuna taudi ꞌidi bubuna guguyoi ta taudi adelidi totoꞌumalidi.   
\p
\v 16 Gosegwao, tetela boboꞌana wagiyai ꞌiꞌisi be ꞌenega yawasi ataya waloba, be tuta nina ꞌiilama yada gwausowala manumi, manuna geya nuwagu be ꞌigu paisewao ꞌemiya ꞌadi mudala.   
\p
\v 17 Wate ꞌeguma ꞌiabe ꞌagu talauwalao siloemwawasigu, ꞌatuwa nadigega sitaliyaegu, yada gwausowala tuga, be ꞌomi wate wada gwausowala. ꞌOmi lowa wataliya Yaubada matanaya, tuta nina Yesu waemisena; ta ꞌigu mwawasa ꞌimi taliyao ꞌida loeposeyanedi.  
\v 18 ꞌEnega ꞌilobwenena be ꞌomi maꞌegwao tada egwausowala leleleya.   
\p
\v 19 Yanuwayaina ꞌaene ꞌInapwana Yesu ꞌina lemega sawesawenaya be muliyega tuta gidalina ꞌena Timoti yaetunenawa, be tetelimi ꞌida meꞌe ꞌeguya, be ꞌenega yada gwausowala.  
\v 20 Timoti namo ꞌimi miya boboꞌana manuna ꞌinuwanuwa sinabwana,  
\v 21 \x * \xo 2:21 \xt 2 Ti 4:9-10\x*ta ꞌagu tolemao yaudi taudimo manudi sinuwanuwa, ta nigeya Yesu Keliso ꞌina guinuwa manuna sida nuwanuwa.  
\v 22 Ta Timoti wamwalatonina ꞌaene tai boboꞌana, ta ꞌatuwa nadigega natugu maꞌiyagu tetela boboꞌana manuna ꞌaetaetapewa.  
\v 23 ꞌEnega ꞌabo tuta nina ꞌagu loina yanonoi, nuwanuwagu be Timoti nina yaetunenawa ꞌemiya.  
\v 24 Ta wate yaemisa ꞌaene ꞌInapwana ꞌina lemega tuta gidalina be ꞌaboꞌagu wate yawawa ꞌemiya.   
\p
\v 25 \x * \xo 2:25 \xt Pi 4:18\x*Ta gete tuga ꞌigu nuwanuwa ꞌaene ꞌilobwenena be Epapilodito yaetune ilenawa ꞌemiya, tauna tasigu ta maꞌiyagu ꞌapaipaisewa, ꞌatuwa nadigega ꞌalosalosaiya Yesu Keliso manuna. Epapilodito nina lowa ꞌagu lema ꞌemiyega ꞌimeꞌena,  
\v 26 ga gete tuga nuwanuwana ꞌomi, ga tuta nina ꞌina leꞌoasa alena ꞌiwai ga wanononaya, bada tauna ꞌinuwamwau ꞌaene geyaꞌabo ꞌomi waꞌateꞌate saꞌala ꞌina leꞌoasa manuna.  
\v 27 Onaꞌaiꞌaila, niꞌatu ꞌileꞌoasa sinabwana, ta saꞌi Yaubada ꞌiꞌatenuwa ꞌoleꞌoleyena, ta wate ꞌaboꞌagu ꞌiꞌatenuwa ꞌoleꞌoleyegu, ꞌabona nai Epapilodito ꞌina mwawasa ꞌenega yada nuwamwau ꞌaiꞌaila.   
\p
\v 28 Gete manuna nuwanuwagu sinabwana be yaetunenawa, be waꞌita limai ꞌaene ma ina boboꞌana, be tauna manuna wada gwausowala, be wate ꞌaene ꞌaboꞌagu ꞌigu ꞌatesaꞌala ꞌigugumwala.  
\v 29 ꞌEnega ꞌabo to tuta ꞌiapwesa ꞌimi senaya, ma imi gwausowala ꞌInapwana ꞌana esanega wada bwauye ꞌimi anuwaya. Be wate ꞌaina ꞌInapwana ꞌina toguinuwao, ꞌabo siwawai ꞌemiya, waꞌamayabedi nadigega Epapilodito.  
\v 30 Onaꞌaiꞌaila, Epapilodito nina Keliso ꞌina paisewa ꞌenaya leꞌoasega selabenaya be ꞌimwamwawasa, manuna ꞌomi nigeya sawesawenaya be walemegu, ta Epapilodito nina ꞌipasima ga ꞌilemegu, ga ꞌenega leꞌoasa nina ꞌilobena.   
\c 3  
\s1 Bubuna boboꞌana manuna  
\p
\v 1 \x * \xo 3:1 \xt Pi 4:4\x*Gosegwao, ꞌilobwenemi wate be ꞌida ꞌInapwana manuna wada gwausowala. Lowa ꞌami loina yaꞌetoladinawa, ta gete watei nuwanuwagu be yada ꞌetoladi limanawa, be ꞌenega wada miya boboꞌana.  
\v 2 Waꞌitaꞌiꞌisimi totoꞌumalidi ꞌidi bubuna ꞌatuwa kedewa, taudi tolodaba ꞌadi bodao ꞌediyega,  
\v 3 \x * \xo 3:3 \xt Lo 2:28-29\x*ꞌAbo Yaubada ꞌena tabwagobwago yaluyaluwana ꞌenega, ga Yesu Keliso namo tatupuna, ta nigeya bubuna baleꞌu ꞌena taemiemisa, gote ꞌenega tamwalatoni ꞌaene niꞌatu lodaba ꞌaiꞌaila taꞌewena.  
\v 4 Onaꞌaiꞌaila, sawesaweguya be esaesa baleꞌu manuna yada onatuꞌe, manuna ꞌaboꞌagu ꞌagu esana tomota yaudi ꞌadi esanao ꞌiloetana sinedi,  
\v 5 \x * \xo 3:5 \xt Lu 1:59; 2 Ko 11:22\x*manuna ꞌaboꞌagu goma Isileli ꞌaiꞌaila, ꞌigu susu Beniamina, ga silodabegu ꞌasiyata eita ꞌigu tubuwa mulinaya, ta Palisiyao ꞌidi loinao yamuliya ꞌaiꞌailidi,  
\v 6 \x * \xo 3:6 \xt Gu 8:3\x*ga yaetapewa sinabwana toekalesiyao ꞌadi gieꞌelouya ꞌenaya, ta nigeya ꞌebweu wate Mosese ꞌina loina yaleꞌoaleꞌoa.  
\v 7 \x * \xo 3:7 \xt Md 13:46\x*Ta esi ꞌagu esana nina sinabwana yaꞌawa yage besobesoena, manuna Keliso namo ꞌena yatagwalegu.  
\v 8 \x * \xo 3:8 \xt Lo 3:21-22\x*Onaꞌaiꞌaila, ꞌigu ꞌInapwana Yesu Keliso ꞌana mwalatoi boboꞌana wawasae, ga esaesa baleꞌu ꞌiboboꞌana sinedi, ꞌenega esaesao nidi yaꞌawa yage besobesoedi, ga Keliso nina manuna yage maiboꞌadi yaloseyedi ga yaꞌawa toꞌumaliyedi, manuna nuwanuwagu Keliso namo,  
\v 9 ta wate nuwanuwagu Keliso maꞌiyagu ꞌada miyami, nigeya ꞌaene taugu ꞌigu bubuna palupalunega, nai Mosese ꞌina loinao ꞌediyega, ta esi emisa Keliso ꞌenaya ꞌenega, nate ꞌida bubuna palupaluna Yaubada ꞌiꞌebwaꞌeda ꞌida emisa Keliso ꞌenaya manuna.  
\v 10 \x * \xo 3:10 \xt Lo 6:3-5\x*Nuwanuwagu wate Keliso yada mwalatoni be ꞌina toololimana ꞌana waiwai yada lotoo, be ꞌina ꞌelouya wate tauna nadigega yada lotoodi, nai ꞌina mwawasa yada etotowane,  
\v 11 \x * \xo 3:11 \xt 1 Ko 15:23\x*be ꞌenega, ꞌeguma kapekapeyana, mwawasega ꞌaboꞌagu wate yada toololimana.   
\p
\v 12 \x * \xo 3:12 \xt 1 Ti 6:12, 19\x*Nigeya ꞌaene niꞌatu toololimana yalobena, nai ꞌigu bubuna niꞌatu maiboꞌana siboboꞌana, ta esi gete ꞌigu ꞌebe masi be ꞌaene yada giyai, manuna yage gete manuna Yesu Keliso niꞌatu ꞌigiyaigu.  
\v 13 Gosegwao, nigeya yaonaona ꞌaene niꞌatu yagiyaina, ta esi ꞌigu nuwanuwa ꞌebweuna namo, ꞌenega yage muliguya yanuwa pupuledi be toꞌase mataguya manudi yatootoo waiwai,  
\v 14 \x * \xo 3:14 \xt 1 Ko 9:24\x*nate ꞌebe masi nina, nai Yaubada ꞌina pali galewaya, Yesu Keliso ꞌenega.  
\v 15 \x * \xo 3:15 \xt 1 Ko 2:6\x*ꞌEnega maiboꞌada gete nadigega tada nuwanuwa leleleya, ꞌabo ꞌida nuwanuwa niꞌatu simatuwa. Be wate ꞌeguma toꞌase manuna ꞌimi nuwanuwa dumadumana, yage nina ꞌalena Yaubada wate maꞌetamo ꞌida eꞌita ꞌemiya.  
\v 16 Ta saꞌi ꞌilobweneda be yage nidi talobediya tagiyai ꞌiꞌisidi.   
\p
\v 17 \x * \xo 3:17 \xt 1 Te 1:7\x*Gosegwao maiboꞌami waetotowanegu, be yaisigedi taudi ꞌidi bubuna nadigega ꞌaboꞌagu waduneduneyema, be ꞌomi wate wada bubuna nadigega.  
\v 18 Ta saꞌi tomota yaudi ꞌidi bubuna ꞌenega Keliso sietalauwalena, tauna manuda ꞌimwawasa kelose ꞌenaya. Talauwalao nidi lowa yasimanedi ꞌemiya, gete tuga wate ma igu dedoi yalolima, toꞌumalina nidi ꞌemiya yasimanedi.  
\v 19 \x * \xo 3:19 \xt Lo 16:18\x*Taudi ꞌidi ꞌebe losalowa sida esilae, manuna ꞌidi ꞌebe emisa gamwapawa manuna, be yage ꞌebe omayamayao situputupudi, manuna yage baleꞌu namo nuwanuwadi.  
\v 20 \x * \xo 3:20 \xt Ep 2:6, 19\x*Ta ꞌaboꞌada esi ꞌida sena galewaya, be gote ꞌenega ꞌada Toꞌetoseyana, tauna ꞌida ꞌInapwana Yesu Keliso, maꞌetamo ꞌiilama, ta tauna manuna tayamwayamwa.  
\v 21 \x * \xo 3:21 \xt 1 Ko 15:28\x*Be tuta nina ꞌiilama ooda ꞌida saꞌugelasedi; batuwa nenetadi, ta ꞌida saꞌugelasedi ꞌatuwa tauna oona waiwaina ta ꞌesasena nadigega, ta ꞌina guinuwa gete tauna ꞌina waiwaiyega, manuna tauna sawesawenaya be yage maiboꞌadi ꞌediya ꞌietoloina.   
\c 4  
\p
\v 1 \x * \xo 4:1 \xt 1 Te 2:19-20\x*Gosegwao niꞌatu nuwagu waꞌewena, ta yaobobomemi ꞌaene ꞌigu ꞌebe gwausowala, nuwanuwagu be loguguya gete wada muliyedi, be ꞌediyega wada toolopaꞌala ꞌida ꞌInapwana manuna, be tauna maꞌemiya.   
\s1 Loguguya  
\b  
\p
\v 2 ꞌOmi iine Yuꞌodia be Sinitiki yasidasida ꞌemiya be wada egosigosiyana limana, ꞌida ꞌInapwana ꞌina nuwanuwa nadigega.  
\v 3 \x * \xo 4:3 \xt Lo 10:20\x*Wate gosiya ꞌaiꞌailigu, ꞌoyo toanugana, yasideyo be iine nidi ꞌulemedi, manuna lowa taudi maꞌegwao ꞌaguiguinuwa leleleya, tetela boboꞌana ꞌana simana ꞌenaya, ta wate Kelemeniti be ꞌaidi wate ꞌagu tolemao maꞌemao ꞌapaipaisewa, taudi ꞌadi esanao yawasi bukina solanaya ꞌetoꞌetoladina.   
\p
\v 4 Tuta maiboꞌana wada gwaugwausowala ꞌInapwana manuna, ta wate yaeona limami ꞌaene wada gwausowala.  
\v 5 \x * \xo 4:5 \xt Ib 10:37; Ye 5:8-9\x*ꞌIlobwenena be tomota maiboꞌadi ꞌimi eꞌalamaꞌiꞌita sida mwalamwalatoni, manuna ꞌiabe ꞌInapwana ꞌiila limanama.   
\p
\v 6 \x * \xo 4:6 \xt Md 6:25; 1 Pi 5:7; Ep 6:18\x*Geyaꞌabo ꞌebweu toꞌase manuna wanuwanuwa, ta esi ma imi lokagutoki yage maiboꞌadi manudi, Yaubada ꞌena wada bwagobwago, be ꞌimi nuwanuwao manudi wada sidasida,  
\v 7 \x * \xo 4:7 \xt Yo 14:27\x*be Yaubada ꞌina lemao tosinabwa sadi ꞌediyega ꞌida giegwausowalimi, be ꞌenega Yesu Keliso maꞌemiya, ꞌatemi be ꞌimi nuwanuwao sida miya boboꞌana.   
\p
\v 8 Gosegwao, gete ꞌebweu wate loguguya ꞌaene wada nuwanuwa yage ꞌaiꞌailidi ma ꞌadi ꞌamayaba manudi, be yage palupaludi manudi, be yage ꞌesasedi manudi, be yage ꞌadi ꞌita kausala nidi manudi, be yage oboobobomidi manudi, be ꞌeguma toꞌase boboꞌana ꞌediya nai ꞌebe tupu ꞌediya manudi.  
\v 9 ꞌOmi wada etotowanegu, ꞌigu guinuwao waꞌitedi ꞌediyega, be ꞌigu onao be ꞌigu eꞌitao wanonodiya ga wamwalatonidiya ꞌediyega. ꞌEnega Yaubada ma ina nuwa siwalowa maꞌemiya wada miya gwausowala.   
\s1 Me Pilipai ꞌidi oboboma Paulo ꞌenaya  
\p
\v 10 ꞌIda ꞌInapwana nina niꞌatu ꞌigiegwausowaligu manuna gete tuga waꞌatenuwa ꞌoleꞌoleyegu wate. Onaꞌaiꞌaila, lowa nuwanuwami be walemegu ta saꞌi nigeya ꞌebweu wate ꞌeda ꞌimiyami.  
\v 11 Ta geyaꞌabo saꞌi yalomulomugi ꞌigu miya mwau lowa ꞌediya, manuna niꞌatu yamwalatonina ga sawesaweguya miya maiboꞌadi ꞌediya yagwaugwausowala tuga,  
\v 12 nai miyamwau ꞌediya nai ꞌebe gwausowala ꞌediya, nai tuta sesoi nai ꞌabo ma ꞌagu botana, nai ꞌeguma yaeesaesa, nai ꞌeguma yaetogomabeso,  
\v 13 \x * \xo 4:13 \xt 2 Ko 12:9-10\x*sawesaweguya miya maiboꞌadi ꞌediya yada gwausowala tuga, manuna tauna maꞌiyagu ꞌamiyami niꞌatu ꞌigiewaiwaiyegu.  
\v 14 Ta niꞌatu ꞌigu miyamwau gete wagie kapekapeyanena ꞌimi lemega ga manuna yalokagutoki sinabwana ꞌemiya.  
\v 15 ꞌOmi me Pilipai niꞌatu wamwalamwalatoni ꞌaene tetela boboꞌana ꞌana simanaꞌunu ꞌemiya ꞌenaya, tuta nina Masidonia yapilisinena, ga nigeya ꞌebweu ꞌasa ꞌana toekalesiyao ꞌidi ꞌebwayadaita ꞌenega silemelemegu, ꞌadi lema ꞌeguyega ꞌana eꞌisa manuna; ta ꞌomi namo me Pilipai walemegu.  
\v 16 Onaꞌaiꞌaila, tuta nina lowa Tesalonaika ꞌena yamiyami, ꞌagu lema maꞌebweuna ta muliyega ꞌeluwena waꞌebwaꞌegu.  
\v 17 ꞌIgu ona gete nigeya ꞌaene nuwanuwagu ꞌebwayadaita wada ꞌebwaꞌegu, ta esi ꞌaene ꞌimi ꞌebwayadaita uwana ꞌemiya ꞌida sinabwa ꞌami lema ꞌaiꞌaila manuna.  
\v 18 \x * \xo 4:18 \xt Ep 5:2\x*Ta ꞌimi ꞌebwayadaita nina Epapilodito ꞌimeꞌena, maiboꞌana yalobena ꞌimaa tasitasiwa, ꞌatuwa nadigega ꞌimi taliya boboꞌana Yaubada ꞌenaya, niꞌatu wagabuna ga maina boboꞌana Yaubada ꞌimuina ga manuna ꞌigwausowala.  
\v 19 \x * \xo 4:19 \xt 2 Ko 9:8\x*ꞌEnega ꞌigu Yaubada nina ꞌimi nuwanuwao maiboꞌadi ꞌida ꞌebwaꞌemi, nate tauna ꞌina esaesa yau wawasae Yesu Keliso ꞌina guinuwao ꞌediyega.  
\v 20 ꞌEnega ꞌida Yaubada Tamadai nina tada tupu ataya be ataya.   
\p
\v 21 ꞌIgu oboboma Yesu Keliso ꞌina toekalesiyao maiboꞌadi ꞌediya. Ta gosegwao bada maꞌegwao ꞌamiyami wate ꞌidi oboboma ꞌemiya,  
\v 22 ta toekalesiyao taudi Sisa ꞌina anuwaya siguiguinuwa, be toekalesiyao maiboꞌadi, ꞌidi oboboma ꞌemiya.   
\p
\v 23 ꞌInapwana Yesu Keliso ꞌina obobomega yaluyaluwami sida miya boboꞌana.  
\cls ꞌAboꞌagu Paulo.   